===Adjective===
{{en-adj|eeri|er}}

# [[strange]], [[weird]], [[fear]]-inspiring.
#:''The '''eerie''' sounds seemed to come from the [[graveyard]] after [[midnight]].''
# [[fearful]], [[timid]].

